  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_7' aria-label=\" Sheikh Javeed Ahmad & Anr. versus State of J&K & Ors. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('7','2025','2025_3_1503_1518','2025INSC624'); ><font size='4'> <strong>SHEIKH JAVEED AHMAD & ANR.<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>STATE OF J&K & ORS. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 3 S.C.R. 1503</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 624</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010004762025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : VIKRAM NATH, SANJAY KAROL, SANDEEP MEHTA</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Whether the High Court erred in setting aside the appointments of the appellants as Assistant Professors as being incompatible with the rules and regulations. Headnotes&dagger; Service Law &ndash; High Court canceled the appointment of the appellants as Assistant of Physical Medicine &amp; Rehabilitation (PMR), Sher-I-Kashmir Institute of Medical Sciences, Soura, Srinagar (SKIMS) holding that they did not have the prescribed qualification of diploma course in PMR &ndash; It was held that they did not make any effort for admission into the<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 27-03-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CIVIL APPEAL No. 4426/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Appeal(s) allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 3 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('7','2025','2025_3_1503_1518','2025INSC624','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('7','2025','2025_3_1503